    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ きど・こういち ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n内相、厚相、文相、内大臣、宮内省参事官、<a href=\"../p/kgentaro.html\">児玉源太郎</a>の女婿、木戸孝允の養子の子、Ａ級戦犯"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "hidden"
   },
   "html": "<a name=\"s1\"></a>\n<a href=\"#s1\">＝</a><a href=\"#h\">△</a><a href=\"#h\">◎</a><a href=\"#s2\">▽</a><a href=\"#s1\">＝</a>"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　東京出身。木戸孝允の養子、侯爵木戸孝正の長男。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　学習院に学び、京都帝大法学部を卒業後、農商務省に入省。襲爵し貴族院議員。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　内大臣秘書官長など歴任後、<a href=\"../1937/kono1_1.html\">近衛内閣①</a>の文相兼厚相に就任。ついで<a href=\"../1939/hira_1.html\">平沼内閣</a>の内相。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　内大臣就任後、天皇側近として次第に国政の実権を握る。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　重臣会議で主導性を発揮し、<a href=\"../1941/tojo_1.html\">東條内閣</a>の成立に尽力。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、Ａ級戦犯として東京裁判で「終身禁固」の判決を受ける。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
